On DB Server with orasid:
brconnect -c -u / -p initF4E.sap -f chpass -o SAPDAT -password MhQT158ISFdxab_b

on sap instances with sidadm:
rsecssfx put DB_CONNECT/DEFAULT_DB_USER SAPDAT -plain
rsecssfx put DB_CONNECT/DEFAULT_DB_PASSWORD MhQT158ISFdxab_b
rsecssfx list

For Java system also check configtool
